id-21574.title: Life Coach
id-21574.post-content:
The Life Coach template is a simple, effective design that enables your content to take center stage. It’s a welcoming template with a static image header with headline and clear content and service areas down the page to help tell your story.

The template offers a range of flexible elements and pages you can customize to your particular needs without losing the overall appeal. The theme works seamlessly with WooCommerce and includes a product page so you can sell merch as soon as you launch.

Key features of the Life Coach template

  • Effective design ideal for life coaches and the wellness niche
  • Flexible pages and content areas can be easily personalized
  • Integrates with WooCommerce for selling online
  • Great use of images, content areas and layout
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-21574.post-excerpt: Effective web design that can be fully customized for life coaches or wellness

id-47529.title: Roofing Services
id-47529.post-content:
The Roofing Services web template is a bright and breezy business design that welcomes you with open arms. It opens with a fullscreen image with bright colors and white headline that sets the scene perfectly. It could be used for literally any type of business.

The design is light and easy to use, with modern fonts, lots of whitespace, a contact form front and center, creative product and service section and supplementary pages. It’s a very composed design that inspires confidence, ideal for business use.

Key features of the Roofing Services template

  • Bright and breezy design suitable for many types of business
  • Excellent layout with customizable content areas
  • Contact form front and center
  • Supplementary pages ideal for business
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-47529.post-excerpt: Bright and breezy web template suitable for almost any business you can think of

id-57190.title: Luxury Hotel
id-57190.post-content:
The Luxury Hotel template uses a dark design and gold color to create a feeling of elegance and luxury. It includes an attractive slider to paint the picture of a lifestyle and a parallax effect with hotel images as the background. All designed to help sell rooms.

The template includes typical content areas for a hotel including for rooms, amenities, dining and more. Each can be fully customized to suit your particular hotel, as can the portfolio, blog area and individual room and amenity pages. It’s the only hotel template you need!

Key features of the Luxury Hotel template

  • Elegant website template ideal for luxury hotels
  • Dark and gold colors create an exclusive feel
  • Lots of opportunities for images to help sell
  • Relevant content areas and pages for hotels
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-57190.post-excerpt: Elegant web template ideal for luxury hotels, travel and big ticket items

id-47585.title: Freelance Copywriter
id-47585.post-content:
The Freelance Copywriter template works as a business website or online resume depending on how you configure it. It’s a relaxed design with lots of white space and calm complementing colors.

The design includes plenty of opportunities to highlight skills and experience as well as products and services. There’s an engaging call to action, milestone and awards section, a portfolio page, testimonials page and an attractive contact page. Everything the budding freelancer needs to grow their business.

Key features of the Freelance Copywriter template

  • Configurable resume or business website for freelancers
  • Easygoing design with calm colors and whitespace
  • Lots of customizable content areas
  • Portfolio page already designed and ready to go
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-47585.post-excerpt: Adaptable web template ideal for freelancer and small business promotion

id-51415.title: Pharmaceutical Company
id-51415.post-content:
The Pharmaceutical Company template has a light, inclusive feel that uses colors related to the medical feel to inspire confidence and communicate meaning. Modern fonts, animations and quality images combine with customizable content areas to tell your story.

The template includes lots of space on the homepage to outline products and services and supplementary pages to expand and convert visitors. The overall look and feel of the template is positive and reassuring, just what pharmaceutical companies or the medical profession needs to communicate.

Key features of the Pharmaceutical Company template

  • Reassuring website design ideal for pharma or the medical field
  • Includes lots of content areas for products and services
  • Lots of whitespace helps your message stand out
  • Supplementary pages ideal for the niche
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-51415.post-excerpt: Reassuring website design with some nice touches, ideal for pharmaceutical companies

id-51578.title: Family Lawyer
id-51578.post-content:
The Family Lawyer template is a sober design ideal for an industry like the law. It remains approachable and welcoming though, thanks to friendly fonts and a nice contrast color. The overall design helps create authority and trust, two things a lawyer needs.

The template includes a simple header with a background image and opens up into a white background with borderless content areas to show products, services and specialties. Everything can be customized to suit your business with minimal effort to create something truly unique.

Key features of the Family Lawyer template

  • Modern design that helps build trust and authority
  • Customizable homepage so you can showcase your services
  • Borderless content areas make the page flow seamlessly
  • Extra pages ideal for the legal profession
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-51578.post-excerpt: Modern business web template ideal for lawyers and the legal profession

id-57319.title: Book Store
id-57319.post-content:
The Book Store website template is a focused template designed for small books stores or authors who want to sell directly to the public. It’s a relaxed design with the header section set up to showcase your latest publication.

The template integrates seamlessly with WooCommerce so you can sell digital downloads or physical books from the site. There are customizable content areas throughout and a range of calls to action, image options, testimonials and review options to include if you want.

Key features of the Book Store template

  • Relaxed design that lets products shine
  • Optional extra sections for books and categories
  • Fully compatible with WooCommerce for direct sales
  • Customizable sections and pages for any type of store
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-57319.post-excerpt: Relaxed web template ideal for book stores and authors who want to sell direct

id-47838.title: Online Cooking Courses
id-47838.post-content:
The Online Cooking Courses template makes an instant impact thanks to a colorful header with a strong image and headline. It’s an engaging design that unfolds into a light, white page with lots of options to outline courses and use imagery to sell.

This is an LMS website template that will be compatible with leading learning management systems to help you set up your courses quickly and easily. Course pages are equally well designed and include everything you need to attract new students.

Key features of the Online Cooking Courses template

  • Impactful design with bright colors and strong imagery
  • Light content areas designed for courses
  • Course pages include basic outline all ready to customize
  • Includes enrolment button for quick and easy signups
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-47838.post-excerpt: Vibrant online learning template designed to help make learning fun for everyone

id-49406.title: Freelance Voice-over Artist
id-49406.post-content:
The Freelance Voice-over Artist template could work as a resume or portfolio for musicians and many other professions. It’s a light modern design with strong images, calm colors and very modern fonts.

The template has been configured for musicians but would work for anyone with a little customization. It has flexible content areas with space for images, text, audio or video clips, a biography, testimonials and social media integration. Everything you need to promote yourself.

Key features of the Freelance Voice-over Artist template

  • Modern business theme that works as a portfolio or resume
  • Calm colors and contemporary fonts
  • Great use of images, content areas and layout
  • Supports images, audio and video
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-49406.post-excerpt: Contemporary website template that’s perfect for freelance artists and performers

id-49217.title: Piano Tutor
id-49217.post-content:
The Piano Tutor template communicates its purpose immediately with a thoughtful image and header. The homepage opens out into a light, informative design with areas for courses, specializations, a biography, service area and testimonials, everything a piano teacher might need.

The template uses high quality images throughout to help tell your story, along with flexible content areas, an enrolment form, relevant extra pages and an attractive content page.

Key features of the Piano Tutor template

  • Communicative web template for piano tutors and teachers
  • Well-designed layout with music elements everywhere
  • Flexible content areas with some nice effects
  • Relevant extra pages ideal for tutors
  • Full compatibility with leading page builders
id-49217.post-excerpt: Communicative website template designed for teachers, tutors and instructors
